  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Description&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Software delivery costs&amp;nbsp;can be measured&amp;nbsp;in dollars or effort. Cost contributors for software delivery&#xD;
    include:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Fully Burdened Labor Costs &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Labor&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Charge back for environment (tools and hardware)&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Office expenses&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        License Costs &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                COTS product&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Mentoring&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Third-party labor, including outsourced work&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Training&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Migration&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    To monitor&amp;nbsp;Cost&amp;nbsp;status for a project, see the &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; id=&quot;A_-_-_C:/CCRC_Views/SVL_UMF_Lib_Shared/umf/lib/suppl/perf_meas/practice.mgmt.perf_meas_setup.extend_prac2-ibm/customcategories/cost_87BD2483.html:.:.:&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/customcategories/cost_87BD2483.html&quot; guid=&quot;_LvOBcLQqEd6HgZ8EwRW1Og&quot;>Cost metrics page&lt;/a> which includes a sample dashboard.&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Strategies&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following strategies help reduce the costs associated with software delivery:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; id=&quot;A_-_-_C:/CCRC_Views/SVL_UMF_Lib_Shared/umf/lib/suppl/perf_meas/practice.mgmt.perf_meas_setup.extend_prac2-ibm/customcategories/improve_sw_delivery_efficiency_7D6205A1.html:.:.:&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/customcategories/improve_sw_delivery_efficiency_7D6205A1.html&quot; guid=&quot;_qc8rgLbGEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Improve Software Delivery Effectiveness&lt;/a> &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Streamline software delivery processes, reduce manual work and increase automation&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Reduce costs and effort by increasing design and code reuse, including existing industry standards.&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Indicators &#xD;
                &lt;ul>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        High levels of manual work&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Ineffective procedures, bureaucratic processes&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Low bandwidth communication&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        High communication overhead&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                &lt;/ul>&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; id=&quot;A_-_-_C:/CCRC_Views/SVL_UMF_Lib_Shared/umf/lib/suppl/perf_meas/practice.mgmt.perf_meas_setup.extend_prac2-ibm/customcategories/reduce_infrastructure_costs_58C717B2.html:.:.:&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/customcategories/reduce_infrastructure_costs_58C717B2.html&quot; guid=&quot;_yj7DMMx-Ed6AlLazTePGRg&quot;>Reduce Infrastructure Costs&lt;/a> &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Effectively drive down infrastructure costs associated with legacy applications.&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Indicators: &#xD;
                &lt;ul>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Multiple infrastructures to support multiple platforms (server sprawl) are too costly and difficult&#xD;
                        to maintain.&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Infrastructure cannot extend (additional staff, hardware, software too costly) to support needs of&#xD;
                        the business.&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                &lt;/ul>&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; id=&quot;A_-_-_C:/CCRC_Views/SVL_UMF_Lib_Shared/umf/lib/suppl/perf_meas/practice.mgmt.perf_meas_setup.extend_prac2-ibm/customcategories/modernize_applications_98257AFE.html:.:.:&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/customcategories/modernize_applications_98257AFE.html&quot; guid=&quot;_e-6h8LbGEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Modernize Applications&lt;/a> &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Modernize and streamline the application environment in order to reduce costs and remain competitive.&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Indicators: &#xD;
                &lt;ul>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Applications that no longer serve key business needs.&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Key business functionality that is embedded in brittle, inflexible applications that are not easily&#xD;
                        reused or extended (difficult and expensive to maintain).&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Patchwork of systems and platforms, each with unique maintenance needs.&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                &lt;/ul>&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; id=&quot;A_-_-_C:/CCRC_Views/SVL_UMF_Lib_Shared/umf/lib/suppl/perf_meas/practice.mgmt.perf_meas_setup.extend_prac2-ibm/customcategories/deliver_on_cust_requirements_497F7765.html:.:.:&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/customcategories/deliver_on_cust_requirements_497F7765.html&quot; guid=&quot;_MoRLsLReEd6qwtTa3nKvcw&quot;>Deliver on Customer Requirements&lt;/a> &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Reduce costs and effort by reducing waste, delivering low priority / low value features, or building&#xD;
                something that may not be required&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Indicators &#xD;
                &lt;ul>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        High number of features that have not been used&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Spending money or effort on&amp;nbsp;things not directly related to production&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Large&amp;nbsp;and aging enhancement request backlog&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Large amounts of post-delivery support&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                &lt;/ul>&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/customcategories/optimize_resources_2835D18D.html&quot; guid=&quot;_kvbIALbGEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Optimize Resources&lt;/a> &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Modernize the enterprise for the most efficient use of development and support resources.&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Indicators:&#xD;
                &lt;ul>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Multiple development environments/ platforms with siloed development teams.&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Each development silo requires its own set of development and collaboration tools.&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                    &lt;li>&#xD;
                        Legacy systems require expensive, specialized, hard to find skills to extend and maintain them.&#xD;
                    &lt;/li>&#xD;
                &lt;/ul>&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
